snippet.title: Miley Cyrus Mocks Justin Bieber Hooker Video! Watch!

localized.description:
Miley Cyrus Mocks Justin Bieber Hooker Video Sleeping! Watch full video!! 
http://bit.ly/SubClevverNews - Subscribe Now!

Miley Cyrus Mocks Justin Bieber! We have the full video!
OMG -- Miley and The Biebs are of course good pals, but she's definitely not afraid to poke a little fun at him -- and, that's exactly what she did this week. 
Remember that video that Tati Neves recorded of Justin sleeping during his trip to Brazil? It went viral after everyone thought she was a hooker -- not to mention she confirmed the hook-up days later.  Well, Miley has nowmade a parody video of -- that video.... and in this one, Miley takes the place of Tati and appears to be the one who films it. Her tongue also gets some serious screen time. 
Oh yes, take a look:

Should we rewind and watch that again?  (RWD effect) 

Hilarious.  Miley appeared on the Capital Breakfast Show this week -- after which she outlet posted the video... so we're thinking she obviously filmed it while she was there.
So, I gotta know -- do you think Miley's mock video is amazingly and perfectly hilarious -- or, was it a tad mean-spirited? 
I'm going with funny -- but you should vote below or send me your thoughts on Twitter... and then make sure you like this video and SUBSCRIBE.  Oh, and if you think Miley or JB should be star of the week -- get your votes in! 
IN Hollywood, I'm your host Katie Krause and bye for now!
